Package: interplanet.time
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Interplanetary Time Calculations
Description: Port of planet-time.js to R. Provides orbital mechanics,
    planet time, Mars time (MTC), work-schedule calculations, and
    light-speed communication timing for all planets in the solar system.
    Pure base R, no external package dependencies.
Author: Interplanet Project
Maintainer: Interplanet Project <noreply@interplanet.live>
License: MIT
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
